rows.title: MP : Saddened over offline exams, class 10 student commits suicide

langTitles.en: MP : Saddened over offline exams, class 10 student commits suicide
langTitles.translateTitle: MP : Saddened over offline exams, class 10 student commits suicide

rows.titleEnglish: MP : Saddened over offline exams, class 10 student commits suicide
rows.content:
By RTI

CHHATTARPUR: A class 10 student, who was apparently under stress over his exams being conducted offline, allegedly committed suicide by hanging himself in Madhya Pradesh's Chhatarpur city, police said on Wednesday.

rows.titleEnglish: Ajmer Dargah cleric arrested for offering property for Nupur Sharma's decapitation
rows.content: A cleric of the Ajmer dargah, who on camera allegedly offered his house to anyone who beheads now-suspended BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma for her controversial remark against Prophet Mohammed, has been arrested, police said on Wednesday.

rows.titleEnglish: 138 stranded passengers of SpiceJet leave for Dubai from Karachi in alternate aircraft
rows.content: An alternate aircraft of Indian budget carrier SpiceJet flew to Dubai from Karachi's Jinnah International Airport on Tuesday night, ending a wait of nearly 11 hours for 138 passengers who got stranded here after taking off from New Delhi in the morning.
